.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/project-l-playable-at-evo-2023.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/project-l-playable-at-evo-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/project-l-playable-at-evo-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/project-l-playable-at-evo-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/project-l-playable-at-evo-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/project-l-playable-at-evo-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/project-l-playable-at-evo-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3474201" class="wp-caption-text"> “L 计划”来源：Riot Games</figcaption></figure><p>亚索已确认可以在<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/project-l"><em>Project L</em></a>中玩，这是 Riot Games 即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/league-of-legends-fighter-project-l-will-be-playable-at-evo-2023-3474197">二对二团队格斗游戏</a>。他与阿狸、大流士、卡塔琳娜、金克丝、艾克和俄洛伊一起抵达。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，育碧最新的射击游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xdefiant-delayed-after-failing-console-quality-tests-3496504"><em>《XDefiant》</em>由于主机认证问题而被推迟</a>，执行制作人分享了两个潜在的发布窗口。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/creative-league-of-legends-player-uses-a-wiimote-to-play-yasuo-3496592">创意《英雄联盟》玩家使用 Wiimote 扮演亚索的帖子</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
