 《Lies Of P》删去了“ACAB”的提及，因为它“有点冒险” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/lies-of-p-cut-acab-reference-because-it-was-a-little-risky-3496540?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lies- of-p-cut-acab-reference-因为它有一点风险Imogen DonovanTue, 12 Sep 2023 10:46:46 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPlayStation 4PlayStation 5Xbox OneXbox Series X|S https://www.nme.com/?p=3496540 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们尊重所有可能想玩这个游戏的人”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/lies-of-p-cut-acab-reference-because-it-was-a-little-risky-3496540">《Lies Of P》的帖子删掉了“ACAB”的提及，因为它“有点冒险”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/lies-of-p-removes-acab-reference-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/lies-of-p">《Lies Of P</a> 》是</em>一款受<em>匹诺曹</em>启发的《Soulslike》，删除了游戏中“所有警察都是私生子”（或“ACAB”）的提及，以避免冒犯玩家。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/lies-of-p-preview-believe-the-hype-for-this-bloodborne-inspired-fairy-tale-3452699">“P 的谎言”预览：相信这个受“血源”启发的童话故事的炒作</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<a href="https://videogames.si.com/features/lies-of-p-acab-mission" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《体育画报》视频游戏</em></a>采访时，导演 Ji-Won Choi 承认<a href="https://twitter.com/LittenDraws/status/1557596621407502336" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在斩首木偶上发现的标志</a>最初写着“APAB”。它的本意是被解释为“所有的傀儡都是私生子”，这是对 2020 年乔治·弗洛伊德被谋杀后在抗议活动中流行的反警察短语的一种扭曲。</p><p>根据最近播放的<em>《Lies Of P》</em> ，它现在写着“清除傀儡”，导演解释了为什么这个标志被改变了，尽管他对第一个版本似乎“充满热情”。</p><p> “这是我们要在游戏中使用的信息之一，但我们最终把它删除了，”崔在翻译的帮助下证实。 “我们最终把它取消了，因为我们希望每个人都能按照我们想要的方式享受这款游戏，而不是根据任何趋势来评判。” </p><figure id="attachment_3453201" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3453201" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3453201" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Lies-Of-P-preview.jpg" alt="P 的谎言。信用：Neowiz。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Lies-Of-P-preview.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Lies-Of-P-preview-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Lies-Of-P-preview-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Lies-Of-P-preview-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Lies-Of-P-preview-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Lies-Of-P-preview-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3453201" class="wp-caption-text"> 《P 的谎言》来源：Neowiz</figcaption></figure><p> “我们真的希望我们设计的世界能够被玩家完全按照我们的目标来解释，所以我们剔除了可能有点风险的因素。</p><p> “我们尊重每一个可能想玩这个游戏的人，我们希望每个人都能从中获得最好的体验，”导演总结道。</p><p>当<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/lies-of-p-preview-believe-the-hype-for-this-bloodborne-inspired-fairy-tale-3452699"><em>《NME》</em>在预告中谈到<em>《Lies Of P》</em></a>时，人们对它的压抑环境表示赞扬，尽管表面上看，它与<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bioshock"><em>《生化奇兵</em></a>》的 Rapture 比<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bloodborne"><em>《血源诅咒</em></a>》的 Yarnham 更相似。</p><p>安迪·布朗总结道：“《Krat》给人的感觉怪诞而引人注目：就像皮诺曹在打了太多场比赛后涂在皮诺曹身上的油一样，在我放下控制器后很长一段时间里，我都能感觉到它的印象挥之不去。” </p><figure id="attachment_3401447" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3401447" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3401447" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Lies-Of-P-release-date.jpg" alt="P 的谎言。信用：Neowiz。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Lies-Of-P-release-date.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Lies-Of-P-release-date-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Lies-Of-P-release-date-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Lies-Of-P-release-date-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Lies-Of-P-release-date-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Lies-Of-P-release-date-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3401447" class="wp-caption-text"> 《P 的谎言》来源：Neowiz</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《P 的谎言》</em>将于 9 月 19 日登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps4">PS4</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a> 。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/armored-core-6-fires-of-rubicon"><em>装甲核心 6</em></a>补丁 1.02 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/armored-core-6-patch-1-02-might-make-the-early-game-easier-3496149">似乎使游戏的早期章节变得更容易</a>，增强了各种装甲核心武器，并对 Boss Balteus、Sea Spider 和 CEL240 进行了更改。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/lies-of-p-cut-acab-reference-because-it-was-a-little-risky-3496540">《Lies Of P》的帖子删掉了“ACAB”的提及，因为它“有点冒险”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
